{
  "a2ui_version": "0.9",
  "catalog": "artifact-organizer/v1",
  "is_task_complete": true,
  "parts": [
    {
      "component": "artifact-organizer/Page",
      "props": {
        "title": "Artifact Organizer Codebase Map",
        "subtitle": "How a semantic envelope becomes one self-contained HTML page",
        "toc": true
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "component": "artifact-organizer/Section",
          "props": {
            "id": "overview",
            "title": "Overview",
            "lead": "The model writes structure. The renderer turns that structure into a browser-ready artifact."
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "component": "artifact-organizer/Prose",
              "props": {
                "markdown": "Artifact Organizer is a **catalog-driven renderer**. The important split is simple:\n\n- `plugins/artifact-organizer/spec/catalog.json` defines the contract.\n- `plugins/artifact-organizer/scripts/render.mjs` validates and renders.\n- `plugins/artifact-organizer/scripts/components/*.mjs` turns semantic nodes into HTML.\n- `plugins/artifact-organizer/assets/*` and `plugins/artifact-organizer/themes/*` supply the shared look and behavior."
              }
            },
            {
              "component": "artifact-organizer/Callout",
              "props": {
                "severity": "info",
                "title": "Key idea",
                "body": "The envelope carries meaning, not presentation. That keeps the output predictable and makes the HTML easy to regenerate from the same source JSON."
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "component": "artifact-organizer/Section",
          "props": {
            "id": "render-pipeline",
            "title": "Render Pipeline",
            "lead": "A single pass moves from prompt to validated envelope to static HTML."
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "component": "artifact-organizer/Mermaid",
              "props": {
                "kind": "flowchart",
                "direction": "TD",
                "source": "A[\"User prompt\"] --> B[\"Command or skill prompt\"] --> C[\"Semantic JSON envelope\"] --> D[\"Schema validation<br/>spec/catalog.json\"] --> E[\"Tree walk<br/>scripts/lib/tree.mjs\"] --> F[\"Component SSR<br/>scripts/components/*.mjs\"] --> G[\"Theme + asset bundle<br/>base.css + themes/*.css\"] --> H[\"Self-contained HTML<br/>+ sibling JSON\"]"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "component": "artifact-organizer/Section",
          "props": {
            "id": "core-modules",
            "title": "Core Modules",
            "lead": "The runtime is small, but each layer has a clear job."
